This is a fork of Elliot Hughes speckeysd; additions include:
	added SIGHUP to restart speckeysd
	added support for ~/.speckeys.conf


From Elliot Hughes http://www.jessies.org/~enh/software/x11/

To compile speckeysd, type:

	xmkmf && make

you should have a "speckeysd" binary in the current directory.

To run speckeysd, type:

	./speckeysd ./keys

("keys" is an example file in this directory.)
